HEADWORD: Cookery
<hw>Cook"er*y</hw> <pr>(k⟦oocr⟧k"⟦etil⟧r*⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The art or process of preparing food for the table, by
